# SimplePlots
CURRENTLY IN DEVELOPMENT. Library for the creation of simple linear plots focused on efficiency and preventing memory losses.

---

## Quick Snippet

```python
fig = Figure()
fig.plot([2, 3, 4], [4, 2, 3], color='red', linewidth=7)
fig.show()
```


